content: CFS-T FB filler module Filler modules for sealing unused space within transit frames when high water- and gas-tightness and fire-resistance are required ### Categories: Home > Products > Firestop & fire protection > Cable transit frames and penetration sealing systems- - - ### FEATURES:Features Placeholder for future cable installations Filler modules are supplied as one perforated block and can be easily separated for individual use Applications Penetrations in shipbuilding and offshore applications Penetrations in wind power structures Telecom, Datacenter, Downstream (oil and gas), Petro-Chem, Control Rooms, Healthcare, Emergency Power, Transmission Towers For approval or certificate information, please see individual items. ### TECHNICAL DATA: Approvals: UL Temperature resistance range: -40 - 122 °F Free from: Halogen (halogen content <= 0.1 weight %) Technical Data | Approvals | UL | Temperature resistance range | -40 - 122 °F | Free from | Halogen (halogen content <= 0.1 weight %) | Reaction to fire class (EN 13501-1) | E ### ITEMS- 2014863 - CFS-T FB 12x10/0 filler module - Package Size 18 pc - 2014866 - CFS-T FB 30/0 filler module - Package Size 24 pc - 2014867 - CFS-T FB 30/0R30 filler module - Package Size 16 pc - 2210445 - Blank Filler Blocks Includes 9 Pieces/Box - Package Size 9 pc
